     You can save and load games at any time, using either the Quicksave feature or the Esc-menu.

     For Quicksave use the <F5> key. The game will be saved as "QUICK SAVE".
     For Quickload use the <F8> key. The game saved as "QUICK SAVE" will be loaded.
     
     Using the "Save" and "Load" options in the Esc-menu, you can save games under any names you like.
